title: Skeletal remains found in Arizona confirmed to be missing boy -police
text:
Skeletal remains found in Arizona confirmed to be missing boy -police Wednesday, March 28, 2018 - 00:57 
Police in Arizona confirm that the remains found near a farm in Buckeye are those of a 10-year-old boy who went missing in 2016. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
